snippet.title: Naval Action Review (Early Access) - Worthabuy?
snippet.description:
Naval Action is an exciting, realistic, and beautifully detailed naval combat game immersing players into the experience of the most beautiful period of naval history - when sailing ships ruled the seas.

Greenman Gaming Link - Use this link to purchase your games.
http://www.greenmangaming.com/?tap_a=1964-996bbb&tap_s=6586-4b38de

During the checking out use the code MACK20-MACK20-MACK20 and you could get 20% off your purchase :)
